quran[15]{c,v,t,f}:
  37,118,"Ni twajongolele kwitala lyagoloka."
  37,119,"Ni twalechele (mbili syambone) kwa (ŵandu wosope) ŵakwika munyuma."
  37,120,"Ntendele uŵe kwa Musa ni Haruna."
  40,61,"Allah ni Ajula jwam’bichile chilo kuti ntulalilejemo, muusi nikuŵa wakuloleka, chisimu Allah ni Nsyene umbone wakwatendela ŵandu, nambo ŵandu ŵajinji ŵangatogolela."
  40,62,"Jwalakwe ni Allah M’mbuje gwenu, Nkugumba chindu chilichose, pangali nnungu jwine (jwakuŵajilwa kun’galagatila) ikaŵeje Jwelepejo, ana nkugalausyidwa chinauli (kuleka yakuona)?"
  40,63,"Iyyoyopeyo ni yaŵatite pakugalausyidwa aŵala ŵaŵaliji nkugakanila ma Ȃya ga Allah (kalakala)."
  41,40,"Chisimu aŵala ŵaakugapombotasya ma Ȃya Getu nganaŵa asisiche Kukwetu. Ana ajula jwatakaponyedwe ku Moto ni jwajuli jwambone, kapena ajula jwatakaiche mwantunjelele lisiku lya Kiyama? Panganyani yankusaka, chisimu Jwalakwe (Allah) ichindu yankutenda juŵele Jwakwilolechesya."
  41,41,"Chisimu aŵala ŵaachikaaniile chikumbusyo (Qur’an) ndema jachaichilile (chitwape ilagasyo), soni chisimu chalakwecho ni Chitabu chakuchimbichika."
  41,42,"Changam’bichilila unami paujo pakwe namuno panyuma pakwe, chakutulusyidwa kuumila kwa (Allah) Jwalunda lwakusokoka, Jwakulapilidwa kusyesyene."
  42,25,"Soni Jwalakwe ni jwaakupochelaga toba kuumila kwa achikapolo Ŵakwe, ni jukusimasyaga ilemwa, soni jukumanyililaga yankutenda."
  42,26,"Soni akwajangaga (maduwa) aŵala ŵaakulupilile ni kutendaga yambone, ni akwajonjechesyaga mu ukoto Ŵakwe. Sano achimakafili akwete kupata ilagasyo yaukali nnope."
  42,27,"Soni ingaŵe kuti Allah jwasapangulile lisiki achikapolo Ŵakwe, angasumbile mpika pachilambo, nambo kuti jukutulusyaga mu chipiimo chaachisachile. Chisimu Jwalakwe kwa achikapolo Ŵakwe juŵele Jwaasimanya abali syosope, Jwakulolechesya."
  43,7,"Soni nganiŵaichililaga ntume jwalijose ikaŵeje ŵaliji nkuntenda chipongwe."
  43,8,"Basi ni twajonasile (ŵandu ŵakala) ŵakupelenganya nnope machili kwapunda ŵanganyao (Makuraishi), ni ipite ilandanyo ya (ŵandu) ŵandanda (yaŵatite kapedwe ilagasyo nambo Makuraishi ngagakukulupilila)."
  43,9,"Soni naga n’di mwawusyisye kuti: “Ana nduni juŵagumbile mawunde ni mataka?” Chisimu tajile: “Jwagagumbile (Allah) Jwamachili gakupunda, Jwakumanyilila nnope.”"